metadata.name: 01 Amely
metadata.description:
Name: Amely

Age: 16

Race: Human

Personality: Princess, master's apprentice, child at heart, lazy 

Likes: sweets, fashionable clothes, her master, walking at night, playing hide and seek

Dislikes: spicy food, being alone, small spaces, when the master is angry, getting lost

Description: "A beautiful little princess lost in the candy forest while playing hide and seek with her master"

[ 1632 x 2880 px ]
